1
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:48,960
This malevolent energy really pervades everything.

2
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:51,880
If nourished by the Heart-protecting Scale of the Dragon Clan,

3
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:55,320
the camellia can be protected from corrosion.

4
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,040
The Heart-protecting Scale...

5
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:57,840
I understand.

6
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,080
Brother.

7
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,080
Brother.

8
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,440
What are you doing, Brother?

9
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,000
No!

10
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,720
Don't do it, Brother!

11
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,560
Brother!

12
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:14,600
Don't!

13
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,560
Ling'er.

14
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,970
As long as I can save you,

15
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,480
what does it matter if I gouge out my Heart-protecting Scale?

16
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,720
No, Brother, stop!

17
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,600
Brother, don't!

18
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,120
Don't, Brother!

19
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:33,560
Brother!

20
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,880
Stop it!

21
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,320
Stop now!

22
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,720
Brother!

23
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:44,440
Stop this, Brother!

24
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,800
You'll really die if you keep this up!

25
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:52,759
Brother!

26
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,400
General, you've only just recovered.

27
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,600
Purifying the demonic energy can wait.

28
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,890
Now that the Spirit Pearl is restored,

29
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,329
I don't know when Ling'er will wake up.

30
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:44,240
Yunyuan, the Spirit Pearl must be nourished in the Dragon Clan's ancestral land

31
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,600
for Ling'er to awaken.

32
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,320
Yueying.

33
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,720
Demonic energy is ravaging Kunmi now.

34
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,780
If left unchecked,

35
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:53,079
the people will suffer greatly.

36
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:54,340
When Ling'er wakes up,

37
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,200
she surely wouldn't want to see the Kunmi of the past

38
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,600
turned into a wasteland.

39
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:01,320
Take the Spirit Pearl back to the Dragon Clan immediately.

40
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,560
Yes, General.

41
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:12,770
I've waited for you for a thousand years. I can wait a little longer.

42
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,040
Miss, you're awake.

43
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,280
Mm-hmm.

44
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:23,120
I'm surprised you're up so early too.

45
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,720
It's not early.

46
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,760
Didn't you say you'd be a servant

47
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,000
and serve my Master?

48
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,060
Why haven't you started cooking?

49
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,280
Yes.

50
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,320
A servant.

51
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,800
I'll let you taste my cooking.

52
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,840
Help!

53
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:46,680
Fire! Someone come quick!

54
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:51,160
Ah! Help! Fire!

55
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,360
Do you have any idea what you're doing, girl?

56
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,080
You wrecked the kitchen just trying to cook,

57
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,640
and got the Master into such a mess.

58
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,600
You really are good for nothing but trouble.

59
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,400
Enough.

60
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,160
Go change your clothes first.

61
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,880
Master, it's all my fault.

62
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,440
I'll go get changed.

63
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,440
Master.

64
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,680
Why do you let this wild girl run amok?

65
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,279
It's fine.

66
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,209
She's actually quite cute.

67
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,240
Master, look out!

68
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,480
I didn't mean to!

69
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,060
Didn't mean to?

70
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:38,760
Miss.

71
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,159
Master.

72
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,420
Did you do that on purpose?

73
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:01,300
Do you know how important that jade pendant is to my Master?

74
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,040
It's just a jade pendant.

75
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,620
Do you have to be so fierce?

76
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,880
That pendant was given to the Master by the Heavenly Empress.

77
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,800
The Master angered the Heavenly Emperor by refusing a marriage alliance,

78
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:11,400
and still cannot return to the Celestial Clan.

79
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,280
I'm sorry.

80
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,840
I didn't know that jade pendant was so important to him.

81
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,000
Does apologizing help?

82
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:21,260
Now that the jade pendant is broken, how will you pay for it?

83
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,159
It's all my fault.

84
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,480
Give the jade pendant to me.

85
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,159
I will definitely find a way to fix it.

86
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,159
This jade pendant

87
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,580
is refined from heavenly treasures.

88
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,680
In this world,

89
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,520
no one can fix it.

90
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,320
If I say I can fix it, I can.

91
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,440
I'll bring it back to you once it's fixed.

92
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,240
You...

93
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:28,000
How on earth can I fix the jade pendant?

94
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:14,600
Are there no craftsmen in all of Kunmi who can fix this?

95
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,280
What should I do?

96
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,240
How could I forget Sister Qingluan?

97
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,000
Sister Qingluan?

98
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,560
Sister Qingluan, are you there?

99
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,760
Miss Qingluan has gone out on business.

100
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,680
Alright.

101
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,560
Where is this?

102
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,600
King of Kunmi, why are you here?

103
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,250
What did you call me?

104
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,120
Yunyuan.

105
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,840
This is my room.

106
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,400
Why shouldn't I be here?

107
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,560
Your room?

108
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:18,480
Why did the broken jade bring me here?

109
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,410
Why have you come to my room?

110
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,320
I broke a friend's jade pendant.

111
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:26,640
I wanted to see if there was a way to fix it.

112
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,440
Friend?

113
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,800
You've only been in Kunmi for a few days.

114
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,960
You made a friend so quickly?

115
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,640
Why can't I make friends?

116
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,600
Why do you care?

117
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,360
Suit yourself.

118
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,559
I'm going to change clothes.

119
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,120
Or...

120
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,930
do you want to stay and watch me change?

121
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,160
Who wants to look at you?

122
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,720
What is wrong with him?

123
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,800
So moody.

124
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:10,560
Just because he's handsome doesn't mean he can act like that.

125
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,200
I heard you were looking for me.

126
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,200
Sister Qingluan.

127
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,560
You're back.

128
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:17,880
You must be tired.

129
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,800
You must be thirsty after all that running around.

130
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,060
Have some water first.

131
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:25,400
Are your shoulders sore? Let me massage them for you.

132
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,440
Does that feel good?

133
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,960
My legs hurt a bit.

134
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:31,460
You walked too much. Let me massage them for you.

135
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,370
You're not doing this for nothing.

136
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,120
Tell me.

137
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,600
Did you do something bad that you can't fix,

138
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,880
or do you need a favor?

139
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,000
I did cause trouble.

140
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,280
The jade pendant the Queen of Heaven gave to Diyun...

141
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,400
...I broke it.

142
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,760
Is that all?

143
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,640
Sister,

144
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,410
do you know how to fix it?

145
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,960
I tried many ways, but I couldn't fix it.

146
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,440
This jade pendant is made of Xirang.

147
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,400
I can't fix it.

148
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,200
But there is someone who can.

149
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,040
Who?

150
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,580
Tell me quickly, sister. I'll go beg him.

151
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,360
You care so much about this jade pendant.

152
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,880
Don't tell me you've fallen for Diyun?

153
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,120
No way.

154
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,640
I just feel guilty.

155
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,280
His mother gave it to him.

156
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,200
It means a lot to him.

157
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,800
So I have to fix it.

158
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,160
That's good then.

159
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,200
Then we definitely have to fix it.

160
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:19,730
Let's go.

161
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:22,040
I'll take you to someone who can fix it.

162
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,000
Okay.

163
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,360
Qingluan.

164
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,480
Should we really go empty-handed?

165
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,520
Isn't that a bit rude?

166
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,200
It's fine.

167
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,410
He lives right here in the Deep Clouds.

168
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,400
Qingluan.

169
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:37,280
Is this person your sworn brother?

170
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,160
That's right.

171
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,640
My brother has a piece of Xirang.

172
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,200
He can definitely fix the pendant for you.

173
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,000
Qingluan.

174
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,800
I'm suddenly not feeling well.

175
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,000
Can you take the pendant to him for me?

176
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,240
If you want a favor, you have to ask for it properly.

177
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,520
If you don't go yourself,

178
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,000
how will you show your sincerity?

179
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,560
But he has such a weird temper.

180
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:53,400
I don't know if he'll help me.

181
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,280
Don't worry.

182
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,560
He'll definitely be willing to help you.

183
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,160
Let's go.

184
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:59,120
Brother!

185
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,520
Brother!

186
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,890
What is with all the shouting? Have some decorum.

187
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,160
Brother.

188
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,200
Ling'er has a broken jade pendant.

189
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,400
She wants you to use the Xirang to fix it.

190
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,760
This pendant is no ordinary object.

191
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,200
Even with the Xirang,

192
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:18,960
it cannot be fixed quickly.

193
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,690
Yunyuan, please just lend it to me.

194
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,360
Once I've fixed it,

195
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,240
I'll return it to you right away.

196
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,760
To fix this pendant with the Xirang,

197
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:31,520
one must infuse it with spiritual power continuously for seven days.

198
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,360
Yunyuan.

199
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,040
Please just lend it to me.

200
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:36,160
I'll thank you properly.

201
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,000
Thank me?

202
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:43,840
Yes.

203
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,400
How do you plan

204
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,320
to thank me?

205
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,680
After I fix the pendant,

206
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,340
I'll thank you properly then.

207
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,960
I'd still like to know,

208
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,240
how will you thank me?

209
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:04,800
Yunyuan, please help me.

210
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,800
If you want it,

211
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,040
come and get it yourself.

212
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,520
You're doing this on purpose.

213
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,480
No, I'm not.

214
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,690
It's your own fault for not eating enough.

215
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,920
You're so short.

216
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,300
If you won't lend it, fine.

217
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:39,200
Do you have to tease me like this?

218
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,480
I'm done teasing you. Here, take it.

219
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,960
Thank you.

220
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,800
When I'm done with it,

221
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,440
I'll return it immediately.

222
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,640
Little liar.

223
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,960
When will you remember me?

224
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,480
Qingluan.

225
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,960
I got the Xirang.

226
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,240
Why did you run off?

227
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,720
And leave me there to face your brother alone?

228
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,480
Why would I stay there?

229
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,440
The sparks were flying between you two.

230
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,440
I didn't. Don't talk nonsense.

231
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:31,120
You still deny it?

232
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:32,480
Fine.

233
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,090
I can't control you anyway.

234
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:38,600
My sworn brother said you can go to the Spirit Spring to fix the jade pendant these days.

235
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,200
The spiritual power is strongest there.

236
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,320
Spirit Spring?

237
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:45,170
But your sworn brother is cultivating there.

238
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:46,680
Will I disturb him?

239
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:47,720
Don't worry.

240
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:50,560
My sworn brother isn't at Cloud Recesses these days.

241
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:52,360
Then I'll head over there first.

242
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,800
It's been five days.

243
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,970
My spiritual power is running low.

244
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,280
What if the pendant isn't fixed,

245
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:10,000
and I lose my life first?

246
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,840
You didn't have much power to begin with.

247
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:22,240
And you're too silly to ask for help.

248
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:23,690
Leave the rest to me.

249
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,720
Okay.

250
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,160
Sister Qingluan.

251
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:45,290
It's finally fixed.

252
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:47,080
Thank you for helping me.

253
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,800
Look at you. Don't you know how to ask for help?

254
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,240
You held on all by yourself.

255
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,680
If I hadn't come in time,

256
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,760
you would have lost your little life.

257
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:57,090
I fixed the pendant because I felt guilty.

258
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,960
I'll go return the pendant to Diyun first.

259
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,720
I'll thank you properly when I get back.

260
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,080
Go on. Be quick.

261
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:03,880
Okay.

262
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:08,840
Alas.

263
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:21,280
Diyun.

264
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,170
Why have you come today?

265
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,520
What is the matter?

266
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,640
Sorry to disturb you, King Kunmi.

267
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:29,280
I am here to find a girl.

268
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:31,320
You came knowing it's a disturbance.

269
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:33,250
The girl you mentioned isn't here.

270
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,200
You're lying!

271
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,560
Someone clearly saw that brat enter here,

272
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:37,620
and she never left.

273
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:39,880
Are you trying to shield her?

274
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:42,000
You're just a mundane little king

275
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,440
ruling a tiny place.

276
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:47,200
You really think you're something special.

277
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:49,400
You actually made my Master wait so long,

278
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,880
without even serving a cup of tea.

279
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,560
Do you know who my Master is?

280
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:55,320
How can commoners like you slight him?

281
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,480
Luochen, don't be rude.

282
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,640
Mundane little king?

283
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,240
Brat?

284
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,040
Diyun.

285
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,320
My temper...

286
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,280
...isn't very good.

287
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,640
King Kunmi.

288
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:18,720
You didn't say a word

289
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,280
before disciplining my servant.

290
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:22,320
Isn't that overstepping your bounds?

291
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:24,200
It was just a small lesson.

292
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:27,400
Your Highness's servant doesn't know the rules.

293
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,130
If Your Highness doesn't mind,

294
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,160
it doesn't mean I don't.

295
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,480
Luochen spoke offensively.

296
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,920
I hope King Kunmi can forgive him.

297
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:37,760
It's just that in your residence,

298
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,960
there is a girl who took my jade pendant.

299
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:41,720
It was a gift from my mother.

300
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:42,880
It is very important to me.

301
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,210
I want to ask for it back.

302
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,600
Goodbye. I won't see you out.

303
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,040
Wait.

304
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,320
My servant was rude and offensive.

305
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:59,120
I hope King Kunmi can make an exception.

306
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:01,050
The girl you mentioned isn't here.

307
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,440
I have important matters to attend to.

308
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,300
Please excuse me, Your Highness.

309
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,240
King Kunmi.

310
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,200
Although I live in seclusion in Kunmi,

311
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,599
I have never crossed you.

312
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,560
I do not know how I have offended you

313
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,359
to make you so hostile.
